title: VLUE Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of the iShares Edge MSCI USA Value Factor ETF (Symbol: VLUE) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $79.48, changing hands as high as $79.56 per share. iShares Edge MSCI USA Value Factor shares are currently trading up about 1.5% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of VLUE shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, VLUE's low point in its 52 week range is $67.97 per share, with $89.71 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $79.55.
